#*
# Play a classic beep sound. This is put in a separate script so that it could
# be referenced as a custom action of the Dunst notification system.
#**

#* USAGE:
#*   The script is not supposed to be run directly, but rather by Dunst
#*   notification system.
#**
mpv "${DOTSHARE}/sounds/beep.mp3" > /dev/null 2>&1
